{"hash":"91d4a83f9855c194893a1f5e294057505b0cd33d","data":{"article":{"id":"47f83ab8602bfcb139af5bfdab43a123","title":"How to publish a tool in the Tool Shed","tease":"","category":null,"date":null,"days":null,"contact":"","contact_url":"","authors":"","location":"","location_url":"","source_blog":"","source_blog_url":"","skip_title_render":null,"links":[],"image":"","images":{},"external_url":"","content":"<div class=\"toc-wrapper col-md-3\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#steps\">Steps</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#best-practices\">Best practices</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#use-planemo\">Use Planemo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#follow-iuc-guidance\">Follow IUC guidance</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"body-wrapper col-md-9\">\n<h2 id=\"steps\"><a href=\"#steps\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Steps</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Prepare a correct set of tool files.</li>\n<li>Create an account on the <a href=\"https://toolshed.g2.bx.psu.edu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tool Shed</a>.</li>\n<li>Create a repository.</li>\n<li>Upload your tool files.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"best-practices\"><a href=\"#best-practices\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Best practices</h2>\n<h3 id=\"use-planemo\"><a href=\"#use-planemo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Use Planemo</h3>\n<p>We made the steps above easier to go through by implementing <a href=\"http://planemo.readthedocs.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Planemo</a> for both <a href=\"http://planemo.readthedocs.io/en/latest/writing_standalone.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">tool development</a> and <a href=\"http://planemo.readthedocs.io/en/latest/_writing_publish_intro.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">publishing</a> to the Tool Shed. We <strong>heartily recommend</strong> you use it together with the <a href=\"http://galaxy-iuc-standards.readthedocs.io/en/latest/best_practices.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">best practices</a> for Galaxy tool development.</p>\n<h3 id=\"follow-iuc-guidance\"><a href=\"#follow-iuc-guidance\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Follow IUC guidance</h3>\n<p>The <a href=\"/iuc/\">Intergalactic Utilities Commission</a> maintains a set of <a href=\"http://galaxy-iuc-standards.readthedocs.io/en/latest/best_practices/integration_checklist.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">best practices</a> regarding publishing to the Tool Shed.</p>\n<p>Last but not least we recommend having only tool per repository.</p>\n</div>\n"}},"context":{}}